message.body: Happy birthday Sam~ Hope you had a good day!
Thanks John! I did have a good day. I miss you! How are you?
I'm pretty tired. I had to go to work late and ended up doing 1 to 9ish. I just made dinner now.
Oh gosh, sorry you're feeling so exhausted. I just got home from the Phillies a little while ago. Enjoy your dinner! What did you make?
I made ramen noodles with sunny side up eggs. I should get better at cooking. D:
Well that sounds good to me!
